Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.33,0:00:24.25,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:00.10,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, do you want some jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:02.03,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is a hot dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:02.99,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.33,0:02:05.40,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu, how about some mustard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:06.98,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eating pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.84,0:02:09.85,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I did that on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.18,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's the second day of the Scale Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.18,0:02:15.55,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,What will you be doing, Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:17.75,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I do have some plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:21.12,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's a festival, so you've gotta \Nmake the most of it. Right, Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:22.26,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.44,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking the dog for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:28.87,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about, Miss Isuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.09,0:02:32.61,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be spending the day fighting \Nhordes of paperwork again, Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:33.88,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.19,0:02:37.22,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to help you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.68,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:41.28,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,A mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.55,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Food safety inspections.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.25,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Food safety inspections?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:52.69,Title,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1470,1)}Student of the Mage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:49.97,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Student of the Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:55.15,SignA,S,0000,0000,0000,,Scale Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:58.06,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,This spicy sauce is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what do I eat next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:03.66,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You just want to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:06.11,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you call a "safety inspection"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.52,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, at least tell me the recipe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:14.92,SignB,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}Julius Ripsky/ Person of the Land
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:14.92,Adventurer,,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage Shiyo/ Adventurer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:11.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll pay for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.59,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,You want to steal my unique flavor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:14.92,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.89,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.88,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,They say a festival always has fights,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.93,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,but let's settle this peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.72,0:03:27.31,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,A hamburger feast after a good deed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.59,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Learn some moderation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.68,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a good mood this morning, shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.44,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.02,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,And don't call me shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:39.57,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did something good happen with Shiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:41.95,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:44.40,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:46.01,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:51.21,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This goes way beyond oversized, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:54.22,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Mustard and avocado and tomatoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:57.28,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.46,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.53,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Nice reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.97,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.26,0:04:05.60,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.05,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.13,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.49,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:11.87,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,A stamp card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:13.73,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Each stand you visit will give you one stamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:15.33,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have one more to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:19.73,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:23.74,Rally,A,0000,0000,0000,,Stamp Rally
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:23.74,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,"Get all the stamps, and win a wonderful prize"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:25.97,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the prize is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.50,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a pair of pure white...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.49,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Pure white?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.56,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Lacy pant—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:36.50,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You didn't have to hit me so hard, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.99,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:41.51,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Stupid-tsugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:48.60,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Minori... I'm off to \Ngo help Crescent Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.51,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Tohya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:54.77,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,An assassin with Japanese \Naccessories would look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:05:00.77,SignC,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}For Display
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:04:59.91,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,An invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:04.32,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, for the Twilight Banquet \Nwith Princess Lenessia...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:08.40,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go see Karashin, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.54,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:10.83,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.29,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.10,0:05:16.29,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, why are you inside those boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.42,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It's good for the skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.87,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Minori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:21.94,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:24.30,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Marielle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.55,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,This whole thing was her idea, \Nand now she's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.55,SignC,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}For Display
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:29.16,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:31.81,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:35.06,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu just wanted to eat, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:36.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.82,0:05:41.28,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,With that iron stomach of his, he'd never \Neven know if something were poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.12,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:50.26,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. I don't understand at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.36,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:55.32,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:02.21,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta wanted me to send you over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:04.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Think you could go see what she needs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.01,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.38,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.86,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:11.53,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Your wonderful prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.19,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,All right! That's all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:17.00,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The wonderful prize is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:21.36,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Only one stamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:23.48,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did she switch them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:30.24,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you, shrimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:33.74,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I guess I can just go eat more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.30,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna try to eat until I drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.00,SignC,N,0000,0000,0000,,Crafting Guild \NCouncil Office \N\NKnock First{\c&H1A32BF&}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:39.00,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,That can come later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:41.86,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Can you send some people over here at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.02,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're all booked, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.68,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Man, what a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.68,0:06:48.63,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't talk to him now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Karashin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I brought the reports on the \Nsouth block sales figur—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.27,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.54,0:07:01.74,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're the girl from Shiroe's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:03.59,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:07.03,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Do you want me to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:12.61,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Did the cake buffet yesterday go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:13.68,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:17.36,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Minori's trying to restore Shiroe's reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:21.02,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,His reputation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:25.42,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,He should really step out and \Nshow his stuff a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.92,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,He always just leaves all that to Crusty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:29.77,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.17,0:07:32.68,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,People are good at some \Nthings, and bad at others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.45,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'll simply have to show {\i1}my{\i0} stuff in his stead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:38.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:40.84,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for using a beat-up carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.84,0:07:42.12,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.19,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Just get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.32,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,There's a line forming behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only talking to us that way \Nbecause we're People of the Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.07,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.30,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just telling you not to block the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.30,0:07:55.38,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,This won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:56.58,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Rudy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:59.18,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:02.08,Default,R,0000,0000,0000,,Akihabara's a peaceful place, so no fighting—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.49,0:08:08.84,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time to rest, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:12.30,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You know I'm not cut out for heavy lifting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:15.28,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's busy since we brought \NCrescent Moon Burgers back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:17.85,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,We need to carry this stuff ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.17,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:20.42,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all sweaty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.42,0:08:22.04,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take a bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.77,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:26.73,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:28.66,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt when you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:29.89,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Umeko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:36.09,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We don't have enough men \Nto carry all these boxes for our sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:40.35,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Marie could have just asked you herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's being all hesitant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:44.04,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:46.31,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:47.57,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.40,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:52.05,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But you're talking about me! I can't be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:52.35,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you'll help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.35,0:08:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.06,0:08:57.57,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Marie will be very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:58.92,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:02.90,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so mean to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.88,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not being mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:06.81,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.40,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:10.49,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.16,0:09:14.55,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run away, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:18.07,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be rude to see him when I'm this sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:21.45,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,She's always so honest with herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.83,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.67,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,But I, on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.26,0:09:29.15,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:33.06,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, sure, he's an attractive guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:36.71,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,But he's only the best of \Nall the guys I actually know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.89,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I making these excuses to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.72,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you standing there spacing out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.29,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.70,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Don't surprise me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:48.40,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who called for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.99,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:55.88,Default - italics,H,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I simply act too indifferent...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:57.97,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.37,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,No... Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.64,0:10:04.12,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,This afternoon, we're setting up \Na stand to sell winter clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:08.62,SignD,H,0000,0000,0000,,Crescent Moon Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:08.62,SignE,H,0000,0000,0000,,In Preparations
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:07.22,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love it if you could help out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:08.62,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Winter clothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:11.77,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't planning something again, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:14.55,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just be working in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.55,0:10:17.13,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Then it doesn't need to be me, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:21.57,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe will be coming later...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:25.44,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:28.82,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,What a straightforward personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.02,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Like a puppy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:31.61,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:33.31,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is the life I live!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.44,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}God almighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:45.04,HUD1,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Watermaple Mansion{\fs18}\NJapan Server \NAkihabara \NCity/ No Monsters \NNo PVP\NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:45.04,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do about food?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:49.84,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about adventurers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:53.31,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Could you put some more flowers over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:55.05,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:57.78,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I think that'll basically do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.71,0:11:05.64,Default - flashback,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,It comes with three meals and a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:09.39,Default - flashback,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,It comes with three meals and a nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.76,0:11:13.77,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,He tricked me again. Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:18.41,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's that mean monster's fault that I'm so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:23.78,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,I should remind him which of us \Nhas the greater power here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:26.58,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already well aware of that, so there's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:30.29,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,H-How did...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.99,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Elissa let me through.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:36.80,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:40.23,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,For once, you're actually doing some work,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd come to give sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:46.71,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault do you think this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:51.34,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told the Twilight Banquet was your idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:56.51,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,It's my way of thanking the adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:00.69,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,It was smart to use a number of smaller tables,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:04.04,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,rather than a single big one, \Nwhere people are ordered by rank.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.96,0:12:07.83,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Adventurers dislike the nobles' useless formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:12.08,Default,L,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think I understand that a little now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.03,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:19.89,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he'd make sarcastic comments as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.15,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:29.63,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to figure out what that monster's \Nthinking is a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:31.85,Default - italics,L,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:38.04,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.04,0:12:41.76,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have your own work to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:43.80,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm free today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:45.61,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,But anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All these forms have completely \Ndifferent sizes and layouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:54.70,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,People of the Land have come from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:57.24,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if each territory has its own forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:59.37,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.63,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:03.63,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start by organizing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.13,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:08.76,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Minori, I didn't know your subclass was scribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:11.24,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.18,HUD1,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Minori \N{\fs20}Race/ Human \NShrine Priest, Lv. 37 \NLog Horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.88,0:13:13.77,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I... I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:13.77,HUD1,Sub-class,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}\N\NSubclass \NApprentice, Lv. 21
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:18.99,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to ask you about my skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:22.99,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,You want to change your subclass?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:26.55,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I don't know what to pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.84,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:33.92,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,There's a subclass called "apprentice."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.51,0:13:36.08,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Apprentice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:38.51,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly what it sounds like...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:41.50,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes you someone's apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:46.05,Default - flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,You can become someone's student, \Nand copy their skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.51,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.50,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,But there are limits on which skills you can learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.92,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,You can only gain the skills for your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:56.09,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,But you get a bonus, so it levels up quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.09,0:13:59.41,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,And when you change classes, \Nyou keep your experience points.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:04.21,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Until you decide what you want to do, \Nit might not be a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.72,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:10.22,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become an apprentice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:11.71,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:14.52,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,But you already have your tailoring skill...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:18.01,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't pick that because I liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:19.88,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:23.38,Default - flashback,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, will you be my teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:25.38,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:30.21,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I changed my subclass because \NI wanted to be useful to Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.32,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,If I can be of use to the people of Akihabara,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.32,0:14:38.77,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,it might help my teacher's reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:44.78,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,And for that, I must start by doing \Nwhat I can, one step at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:48.55,Default - italics,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,This is my battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.69,0:14:52.78,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:56.29,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You work fast, Minori!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.98,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shiroe's student, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:02.46,SignF,S,0000,0000,0000,,Linguini
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.75,0:15:04.85,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:07.72,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,The tomato sauce here is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:11.97,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll have enough energy to go back \Nto Crescent Moon this afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:14.11,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,There's the smile I wanted to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.11,0:15:16.82,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.06,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:23.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this stain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.28,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll p-pay for it, so please...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:30.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You could never afford it! Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.38,0:15:34.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I told you it wasn't worth \Ncoming to a filthy shop like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.75,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.47,0:15:38.15,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Is he stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.15,0:15:39.82,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,He chose to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:41.50,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Which of you just insulted me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:47.50,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You three, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.51,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to teach you a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:52.82,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,You want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.01,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,With us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:57.76,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.11,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.82,0:16:04.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:06.38,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.26,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I am a proud member of the cat-people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Never heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:14.06,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Then you really ought to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go... Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.02,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,My lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:22.29,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be mean to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:27.17,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Akihabara has its own rules \Nby which you must abide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:29.68,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you disgrace me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.77,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, control yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:32.65,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you for this, cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.28,0:16:38.93,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:41.05,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:42.94,SignG,Se,0000,0000,0000,,You're just playing around, \Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:47.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A conflict with the People of the Land, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.08,0:16:50.44,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,You might want to beef up security.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.82,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,To a degree, I expected this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:56.70,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,People of the Land live in a class-based \Nsociety, while we're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:58.19,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.57,0:17:02.16,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,All of the People of the Land's traders \Nat this festival are professionals,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:06.21,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,while everyone else running a \Nshop here is an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.01,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,D.D.D. and the Black Swords are available.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:11.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why I have Naotsugu running around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.21,0:17:13.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I think we can leave things alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Team 3 is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Team 2, heading out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.43,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.03,0:17:23.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We assisted one carriage, stuck on a side road,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,halted four arguments,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.86,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,and dealt with two claims of nonpayment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,All involved People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.29,0:17:31.27,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:33.39,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,You've just got to be tough and draw the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.39,0:17:34.99,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Keep at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:35.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:40.03,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't expect to see so many here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:43.00,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure People of the Land \Nlove their festivals, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.50,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:50.51,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe that villain was the one \Nwho brought all this business to Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:55.68,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I once invited him to join my guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.82,0:18:00.73,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,This was after the Tea Party disbanded, \Nwhen he was a solo player.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:04.74,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'd seen how he fought while \Nhe was a guest of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.21,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.61,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,He turned me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:12.70,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't think I'm worthy of the offer," he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.20,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I lost interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:20.39,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not interested in anyone who isn't \Nready to find and slay new enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:24.55,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,And after the Apocalypse, he grew up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:27.65,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,Enough to have an influence on the entire city.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.54,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I don't get...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:34.55,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a strategist? Or a gambler?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.49,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even sure if he feels dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:43.27,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,I think Shiroe is at his best when anything goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.27,0:18:44.52,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,"Anything goes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:48.06,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he's a strategist at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.73,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,When the chips are down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:54.60,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,and you have to do whatever it takes, \Nand there's nothing in it for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:58.40,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,he's as strong as anyone you'll ever see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:03.18,Default,Cr,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a cursed sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.48,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:09.81,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,But now, that cursed sword \Nis buried in paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.40,0:19:12.93,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows when he'll be drawn next?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.95,0:19:16.30,Default,I,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we still have something to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.30,HUD1,I,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Merchant's Hall{\fs18}\NJapan Server \NAkihabara \NCity/ No Monsters \NNo PVP\NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:23.80,HUD1,I,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Silver Plaza{\fs18}\NJapan Server \NMerchant's Hall/ Silver Plaza \NCity/ No Monsters \NNo PVP\NEntry Restrictions/ None \NExit Restrictions/ None
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.49,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:24.56,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,You look great. So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, I can't... I can't even...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.92,0:19:27.35,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't say anything about \Nbeing in a fashion show!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.31,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say I'd be working in the background?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.38,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.19,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,The clothing is the star of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:35.19,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:38.19,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You wear this, Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:42.11,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll look good, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:43.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:47.65,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen this many people \Nin a long time, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'd pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The money isn't the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:57.09,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.27,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:07.22,SignH,K,0000,0000,0000,,Cocoa Brown
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've come all the way from \Nthe far west to buy this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:07.22,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But it's only two items per customer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:13.60,Adventurer,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Nemimi/ Adventurer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:13.60,Sign I,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Constantan/ Person of the Land
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:11.35,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can make you famous across the land!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:13.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:16.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:18.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I understand your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:19.99,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But they feel differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:25.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I've got nothing to say to a young kid like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:26.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:32.48,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You will leave, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.96,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:44.04,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,If he'd bought everything, I wouldn't have \Nthe fun of selling them one a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:46.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.39,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.40,0:20:51.47,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he leave so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:54.40,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how long do I have to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.40,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to do business, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.06,0:20:58.20,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you how many you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:20:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We really can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:01.60,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not moving until you say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:02.18,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:03.53,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,How much do I have to pay for a whole box?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:05.58,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:08.03,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The place is getting rowdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.58,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, more than I'd anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.11,0:21:13.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The People of the Land are acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:15.60,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.11,0:21:17.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get a clear enough picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:21.17,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm missing something...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.05,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.49,0:21:27.66,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going through the paperwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:28.85,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,and something isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:33.18,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Some of the paperwork overlaps, \Nand some of their math is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:36.28,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,There's a huge number of very basic errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.28,0:21:37.19,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:40.94,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Most of them come from People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.58,0:21:42.71,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:44.45,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:46.86,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, what will we do about the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:49.23,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Minori, keep this line open.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:49.95,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:55.51,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki, find Isaac and get \Na report on our security.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:01.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like someone is attacking Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:03.90,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:05.51,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.42,0:22:08.62,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to my office in the guild building.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:10.68,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This may be an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:11.70,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.03,0:22:15.12,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:17.68,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,I let down my guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:19.61,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,All the signs were there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:21.25,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,But I was careless...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:24.56,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Now they have the advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:28.11,SignJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(655,1)\an9}New Spirit Ship \N\N{\fs28}Eagle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.21,0:22:30.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be arriving in approximately thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.59,0:22:34.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to disembark, Lord Marves.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.96,0:24:09.37,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,The town of Akihabara is under attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:11.89,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe senses the enemy, and takes action.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.89,0:24:15.86,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,But his guesswork is off, and his calculations fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.86,0:24:18.14,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,The Round Table faces grave danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.14,0:24:19.84,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,What is the enemy really after?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.84,0:24:23.40,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,In the hour of greatest peril, the strategist \NShiroe begins his counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.40,0:24:25.21,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.40,0:24:30.99,Title,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.78,0:24:27.92,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,We will change the world.
